//*** PROGRAM=AF03 ****
// This application is designed to accept and validate
// selection criteria intended to effect a global update on
// Instock percentage within a Season/Year/Type/Gender Age/Line
// Category/Silhouette/Forecaster Code key combination.
// 
// A parameter record containing the above information will be
// created and a batch job submitted to actually update the
// DACAST.VAFCLR01 and DACAST.VAFSTY01 databases.
// 
// The user may exit to any allowed application via FAST PATH
// or PF key at any time.
// 
//   DATE      NAME    DESCRIPTION OF CHANGE
// --------   ------   ----------------------------------------
// 04/21/93   TDODSO   New application.
// 01-05-94   LREIN    Added warning msg to run long&short calc
// 02-15-95   kj       Xsn->Ysn
// *********************
